      "comment": "TWILIGHT ELEGANCE (4) looks much better placed here coming out of an even run in Listed company at Morphettville, in the market there when a battling seventh. She was a winner three back when in this grade and should be very hard to run down here. OMAMORI (3) presents third up and ready to fire, off a good effort at Warrnambool last time when third this level. Up to 2400m should suit nicely now and he can improve again. NASSAK DIAMOND (2) ran well fresh at Pakenham and any rise in trip will only suit the promising jumper. CAPTAIN ELECTRIC (1) hasn't fired in two runs this time in but could be an improver with best figures stacking up well.",
